description:
James from the Warhammer+ army painting team joins Ollie in the studio. Ollie shares some of his favourite ways to paint Tactical Space Marines, while James shows just how easy it is to paint the huge Saturnine Dreadnought.

If you enjoyed this and want to learn more, our YouTube channel has an array of beginner-friendly videos to get you started.

author: Warhammer
description:
James from the Warhammer+ army painting team joins Ollie in the studio to share his insights on painting armour and how certain techniques can help you get your armies ready for battle in no time. From overbrushing to all-over shades and using Contrast paints, you can quickly paint miniatures that you can be proud of.

If you enjoyed this and want to learn more, our YouTube channel has an array of beginner-friendly videos to get you started.
